86 void nimbus::cloudKeypoints<PointInType>::cloudISSKeypoints(const PointCloudConstPtr blob)
87 {
88  double resolution = this->computeCloudResolution(blob);
89  tree.reset(new pcl::search::KdTree<pcl::PointXYZI> ());
90  pcl::ISSKeypoint3D<PointInType, PointInType, NormalType> iss;
91  iss.setSalientRadius(6 * resolution);
92  iss.setNonMaxRadius(4 * resolution);
93  iss.setMinNeighbors(5);
94  iss.setThreshold21(0.975);
95  iss.setThreshold32(0.975);
96  iss.setNumberOfThreads(4);
97  iss.setInputCloud(blob);
98  iss.setSearchMethod(tree);
99  keypointOut.reset(new pcl::PointCloud<PointInType>());
100  iss.compute(*keypointOut);
101 }
